snippet.title: Best VGM 848 - Digital Devil Saga - Svadhisthana
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 612 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AISrz88SJNI
Best VGM 1960 - https://youtu.be/fWx4q8GqZeo

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Shin Megami Tensei: Digital Devil Saga (2005)
Svadhisthana
Shoji Meguro
